Avocado and Corn Guacamole

10 min
$6.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

Description

A creamy and refreshing guacamole with a sweet twist from corn, perfect for dipping or spreading.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • sweet corn (canned or frozen): 1 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • red onion, finely chopped: 1/4 cup
  • fresh cilantro, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • jalape√±o, finely chopped (optional): 1 tablespoon
